OL,3,CDoctors express 'deep discontent' with
OL,4,CManx Care in BMA survey
OL,6,FA survey conducted by the British
OL,7,FMedical Association has revealed
OL,8,Fdoctors in the Isle of Man are 'deeply
OL,9,Fdiscontent' with Manx Care.
OL,11,FThe results showed a lack of
OL,12,Fconfidence in management, a poor
OL,13,Fculture, and overall low morale.
OL,15,FThe 'Culture of Care Barometer'
OL,16,Fcollected 82 responses, after being
OL,17,Fsent to all 155 doctors working
OL,18,Fdirectly for Manx Care.
