OL,3,CDoctors express 'deep discontent' with
OL,4,CManx Care in BMA survey
OL,6,FOf those who responded, only 15% would
OL,7,Frecommend Manx Care as a good place to
OL,8,Fwork, and 81% disagreed with the
OL,9,Fstatement "Manx Care has a positive
OL,10,Fculture".
OL,12,FIn a free text section of the survey,
OL,13,Fone doctor said, "Senior managers need
OL,14,Fto come and follow a shift on Monday
OL,15,Fmorning in theatres to experience how
OL,16,Fthe system is failing patients."
OL,18,FAnother said: "Doesn't matter. No one
OL,19,Fis going to listen. It's pointless
OL,20,Fmentioning anything."
