OL,3,CDoctors express 'deep discontent' with
OL,4,CManx Care in BMA survey
OL,6,FDoctors said they felt 'over-stretched
OL,7,Fand under-resourced', with 67%
OL,8,Fbelieving they do not have the
OL,9,Fresources they need to do a good job,
OL,10,Fand only 20% agreeing that they have
OL,11,Fsufficient time to do their job well.
OL,13,F77% of respondents to the survey
OL,14,Fdisagreed that Manx Care managers know
OL,15,Fhow things really are, and only 9%
OL,16,Fbelieve that the trust listens to
OL,17,Fstaff views.
OL,19,FMore than half also strongly disagree
OL,20,Fthat Manx Care values the service
OL,21,Fdoctors provide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
