OL,6,F"The culture that doctors work in is
OL,7,Fintrinsically tied to the quality of
OL,8,Fcare they are able to give, so these
OL,9,Fresults should concern us all. The BMA
OL,10,Fis committed to working with Manx
OL,11,Fdoctors to help them organise and
OL,12,Fadvocate for themselves in their
OL,13,Fworkplace ` we hope the management of
OL,14,FManx Care are ready to work with us."
