OL,3,CDoctors express 'deep discontent' with
OL,4,CManx Care in BMA survey
OL,6,FChair of the Isle of Man Medical
OL,7,FSociety, Dr Prakash Thiagarajan said:
OL,8,F"Following previous barometer of care
OL,9,Fsurveys we've been hopeful that poor
OL,10,Fresults could act as a catalyst for
OL,11,Fchange, but after this third set of
OL,12,Fresults showing that doctors are
OL,13,Ffrustrated, overworked, and crucially,
OL,14,Fdon't feel listened to, we're losing
OL,15,Ffaith that Manx Care has the will to
OL,16,Fchange things.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
