OL,3,CDoctors express 'deep discontent' with
OL,4,CManx Care in BMA survey
OL,6,F"We hope to be proven wrong, for the
OL,7,Fsake of doctors who deserve better
OL,8,Fworking lives than this ` and for
OL,9,Fpatients on the Isle of Man who must
OL,10,Freceive the best care possible."
OL,12,FManx Care say they are 'disappointed
OL,13,Fwith the results', adding that the
OL,14,Fsenior team are 'actively engaged'
OL,15,Fwith doctors.
OL,17,FThey said the organisation has
OL,18,F'successfully attracted permanent
OL,19,Fmedical staff' over the past couple of
OL,20,Fyears, during a 'financially
OL,21,Fchallenging' time.
