OL,3,CDoctors express 'deep discontent' with
OL,4,CManx Care in BMA survey
OL,6,FThis includes restricting money
OL,7,Favailable to negotiate pay settlements
OL,8,Ffor doctors, which remains unresolved.
OL,10,FAfter discussions with the BMA, the
OL,11,FManx Care Board agreed to pay 6% for
OL,12,Fthe last year, but acknowledged that
OL,13,Fthis does not end the pay dispute.
OL,15,FManx Care concluded: "We hear the
OL,16,Ffrustration of some of our medical
OL,17,Fworkforce and will work closely with
OL,18,Fthem to resolve the issues raised
OL,19,Fwherever we can."
